Condone absence of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>t</mi></math>.</p>\n<p>Only accept&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mrow><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>q</mi></msubsup><mi>v</mi><mfenced><mi>t</mi></mfenced><mo> </mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;if&nbsp;their value of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi></math> does not result in the particle changing direction in the first <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi></math> seconds.</p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>68302</mn><mo>…</mo></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>68</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Special Cases: <br>Award a maximum of <strong><em>(M1)(A1FT)A0FT</em></strong> if the candidate obtains&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>62320</mn><mo>…</mo></math>&nbsp;in part (a), and uses that value to find the total distance to be&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>38302</mn><mo>…</mo></math>&nbsp;(<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>37644</mn><mo>…</mo></math>&nbsp;from 3sf).</p>\n<p>Award <strong><em>(M1)(A0)A1</em></strong> if the candidate writes&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>73</mn><mo>…</mo></mrow></msubsup><mi>v</mi><mfenced><mi>t</mi></mfenced><mo> </mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>t</mi></math>&nbsp;followed by the correct answer.</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 2</strong></p>\n<p>recognition that total distance travelled is the difference between the initial displacement and the displacement at minimum&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>initial displacement is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>38302</mn><mo>…</mo></math>&nbsp;AND at minimum is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>3</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em>&nbsp;<br>total distance travelled <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>38302</mn><mo>…</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>68302</mn><mo>…</mo></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>68</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>If no working shown, award<em><strong> (M1)(A0)A0 </strong></em>for&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>7</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>7</mn></math> (2sf).</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em>&nbsp;</p>","meta":{"questionId":"14859700","referenceCode":"23N.2.AHL.TZ2.4b","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Find the total distance that the particle travels in the first q seconds.","paper":"2","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 5 —Calculus","Topic 5 —Calculus","SL 5.9—Kinematics problems","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.3—Graphing"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}